    "lyrics_en": "Cry, viola\nAnd cry, viola, cry,\nCry, viola.\nCry\nCry, viola.\nCry\nCry, viola.",
    "tip": "A short lament calling for the viola (berimbau) to weep, often sung during Angola games as a moment of reflection.",
